hensive view of prevention and deterrence.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Dez 2019) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Criminology.2bisacsh1 aCaplan, Joel M., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut.1 aPiza, Eric L., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook-Package 2016-2018z978311063539308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook-Package 2018z978311066767708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCal Press eBook Package Frontlist 2017-2018z978311065859040uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520968349zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/doc/cover/9780520968349.jpg  a978-3-11-063539-3  UC Press eBook-Package 2016-2018c2016d2018  a978-3-11-065859-0  UCal Press eBook Package Frontlist 2017-2018c2017d2018  a978-3-11-066767-7  UC Press eBook-Package 2018b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles